As we reported
earlier, the prominent
‘Thriller’ jacket of renowned King of Pop Michael Jackson that was up for auction has
sold for a handsome amount of $1.8m (£1.1m). The auction was held at Julien’s Auction Gallery,
Beverly Hills. The amount is dramatically more than the estimated bid of
